  "range-cache-file:///Users/govind/Documents/PortFolio/kcs-govindtank/styles/dark-theme-palette.md": "[{\"originRange\":{\"start\":{\"line\":0,\"character\":0},\"end\":{\"line\":13,\"character\":0}},\"modifyRange\":{\"start\":{\"line\":0,\"character\":0},\"end\":{\"line\":13,\"character\":0}},\"action\":\"None\",\"isLine\":false,\"originText\":\"Dark Theme Color Scheme\\\\n\\\\n- Background: #0a0a0a (root: --bg)\\\\n- Text: #f1f5f9 (root: --text)\\\\n- Muted Text: #cbd5e1 (root: --muted)\\\\n- Panel Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06) (root: --panel)\\\\n- Panel Border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12) (root: --panel-border)\\\\n- Accent A (Orange): #f97316 (root: --brand-a)\\\\n- Accent B (Light Orange): #fb923c (root: --brand-b)\\\\n- Accent C (Amber): #f59e0b (root: --brand-c)\\\\n\\\\nNotes\\\\n\\\\n- Contrast ratios exceed WCAG AA for text on background and within buttons/cards.\\\\n- Buttons and tabs use orange gradients for high-contrast focus and hover states.\\\\n- Hero parallax and 3D background use muted accents to avoid distraction and maintain readability.\\\\n\",\"originAcceptText\":\"Dark Theme Color Scheme\\n\\n- Background: #0a0a0a (root: --bg)\\n- Text: #f1f5f9 (root: --text)\\n- Muted Text: #cbd5e1 (root: --muted)\\n- Panel Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06) (root: --panel)\\n- Panel Border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12) (root: --panel-border)\\n- Accent A (Orange): #f97316 (root: --brand-a)\\n- Accent B (Light Orange): #fb923c (root: --brand-b)\\n- Accent C (Amber): #f59e0b (root: --brand-c)\\n\\nNotes\\n\\n- Contrast ratios exceed WCAG AA for text on background and within buttons/cards.\\n- Buttons and tabs use orange gradients for high-contrast focus and hover states.\\n- Hero parallax and 3D background use muted accents to avoid distraction and maintain readability.\\n\",\"originTextLength\":673,\"aiScene\":\"builder\",\"behaviorType\":\"accept\",\"updateTime\":1767022172218}]"
